原因: 以不被捕不受傷為大前題，同狗方硬碰硬係無勝算，裝備訓練各方面都輸曬。不過黑警弱點好明顯。裝備厚重、部署時期長，耐力低。每次出動至少幾個鐘，相當於一個跑唔郁嘅大隻佬。所以死守一個地方幾個鐘係無用，要以速度對抗力量<br />\n<br />\nQ. 啲狗一黎，無人守嘅路障立即被秒殺，有撚用？<br />\n<br />\nA. 路障可以即刻拆，但噴黑左嘅交通燈無得即刻處理。而且透過不停制作路障，大大增加狗方需要嘅覆蓋範圍，等於迫班防暴速龍係咁跑<br />\n<br />\n結語: 避其鋒，攻其短，絕不能再犧牲勇武派！<br />\n<br />\n利申：FF"},{"pid":"c2448c6bf5eb5001efc4a61a35e56c7e27653775","tid":1388521,"uid":130406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141021/large/21ec1p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141021%2Flarge%2F21ec1p3.jpg&h=74bceb75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"600feb124e53a4bbb1d8ab4dc73c6714de75775b","tid":1388521,"uid":14220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1034be6d2f7db43d46736c7d3553339f2e83e6a2","tid":1388521,"uid":48579,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"勾腳啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"推呢個，勾腳拖低佢"},{"pid":"6b059a33e6afff69322617015daed510a3757f81","tid":1388521,"uid":130406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1034be6d2f7db43d46736c7d3553339f2e83e6a2","tid":1388521,"uid":48579,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"勾腳啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"可以下次推post用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">發夢用遮勾狗腳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}